Module WitchHunt

Package fr.sos.witchhunt.view.gui

package fr.sos.witchhunt.view.gui

This package contains all classes of the Graphical User Interface view.

Central class for display : GUIView.

Input is collected by the controllers of the fr.sos.witchhunt.controller and fr.sos.witchhunt.controller.interactions packages.
